h.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1DfvwN.jpg&h=6f8fb244&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2riOQwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2riOQwO.jpg&h=074cd595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCaEXbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCaEXbO.jpg&h=0736be80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=3577dc44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"0ca7b57420318b7c9f19a5089a2e06bfad671e0c","tid":1565810,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"277212a63e2717e22a1f93961a42d2e66f3752b3","tid":1565810,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ea5414e87ed0f41b7eed9b2459ee63146ca3dcc","tid":1565810,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"6ef0a17c44ba3e7df6f1558ec65692de1b0d7056","tid":1565810,"uid":310960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"Dllm 以後都咪撚出街啦on9"},{"pid":"82156bc8961